mtn: mtn (Movie Thumbnailer)
mtn:
mtn: Movie Thumbnailer (mtn) saves thumbnails (screenshots) of movie or
mtn: video files to jpeg files. It uses FFmpeg's libavcodec as its engine,
mtn: so it supports all popular codecs, e.g. h.265/hevc, h.264, AV1, VP9,
mtn: mpeg1, mpeg2, mp4, vc1, wmv, xvid, divx.
